ticket_classes.name: Youth 8-12
ticket_classes.description:
Full membership for children age 8-12. Must be chaperoned by an adult age 18+ who has a Underwater Basket Weaving Expo paid membership.
** First Name, Last Name and Email address MUST be the adult member's information. We only require the Child's badge name.

ticket_classes.name: Small T-Shirt
ticket_classes.description: The shirt is a black t-shirt with this year's art.
ticket_classes.order_confirmation_message: The preordered shirt can be picked up at the Underwater Basket Weaving Expo: Underwater Basket Weaving Expo merchandise booth during the normal dealer room hours. You must bring a copy of your invoice or have it on your phone for staff to view to pick up your shirt. Any shirts not picked up prior to close of Dealer Room on Monday of the convention are forfeit and non-refundable.
